				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Shadowheart, Lae'zel and Gale converse while travelling. Shadowheart asks what happens if Lae'zel hopes of being cured at a gith creche don't work out. Lae'zel doesn't even want to consider such an option. Gale chimes in, saying that Baldur's Gate will be their best chance - many skilled people are drawn there."
				}
